Detailed Description

Adds this system to the list, then it adds the following in order: 1) all of its inports 2) all of its subsystems 3) all of its ouports 4) all of its lines.

In this way we make sure that all references are defined before they are used. The ordering of subsystems between the ports has to do with how SystemLayouter works.
